<item>
            <title>[FLINK-3390] Savepoint resume is not retried</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/FLINK-3390</link>
                <project id="12315522" key="FLINK">Flink</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;When during resuming from a savepoint, restoreState fails for a task node, job is retried but without retrying resume from savepoint state. This leads to the job being restarted with empty state. &lt;/p&gt;</description>
                <environment></environment>
        <key id="12938528">FLINK-3390</key>
            <summary>Savepoint resume is not retried</summary>
                <type id="1" iconUrl="https://issues.apache.org/jira/secure/viewavatar?size=xsmall&amp;avatarId=21133&amp;avatarType=issuetype">Bug</type>
